      "writtenOn": "2026-03-10T07:30:17Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yes, `Members` can be accumulated in this path, so we should not reset it on io_error.\n\nFor the legacy path without the aggregator enabled, I think the old behavior would still be fine. However, when the aggregator is enabled on a platform, two response resources are merged. If we reset the array here, the entries from the aggregated response may be lost.",
